    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform. It features a naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, mechanical engagement, paired with a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains structurally flawless, exhibiting exceptional lateral rigidity with no fatigue at the rear subframe mounting points. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory depth and clear-coat integrity, while the cabin displays zero bolster wear or electronic pixel degradation. A concourse-level specimen with a meticulously documented service history.",
