      "description": "Presented for the most discerning collector, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of preservation. The exterior is finished in its original, mirror-like paint, free of rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, and has been protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. Every body panel is perfectly aligned with factory-tight gaps. Step inside to an interior that remains in showroom state; the premium leather bolsters show zero signs of entry wear, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty liners since day one, and the cabin still retains its distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, operates with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is flawless. It has been maintained exclusively by certified master technicians with a 'no-expense-spared' philosophy, evidenced by a comprehensive folder of service records. The engine bay is detailed to a concours standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its life in a climate-controlled garage. Included in the sale are both original master keys, all factory manuals in their leather bound case, and the original window sticker. This is not just a used car; it is a time-capsule example for a buyer who demands perfection.",
